  <div class="card">
    <h2>Reflection</h2>
    <p>
      Working on SYLTrack strengthened my understanding of how design decisions impact maintainability and user experience.
      This artifact helped me practice improving an existing codebase by identifying weaknesses, refining structure, and making targeted changes
      that provide clear value. A challenge in this process was balancing usability improvements with keeping the code organized and easy to maintain.
      Overall, enhancing SYLTrack reinforced the importance of thoughtful design, iteration, and clear communication in professional software development.
    </p>
